thread.title: Aldo Violo

author: Aldo Violo
title: Aldo Violo
text:
the cost of the car with unlimited mileage was very acceptable. But what they fail to tell you is that your Countries insurance plane will not work and you must pay $464.oo with $1900.00 deductible or $564.oo full coverage. The cost of the car for the week was a hell of a lot more than a bus I could of taken. Believing the total cost of the car fooled me into taking it. Next time not a chance.
Aldo Violo
